### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/health

###
### Create a Review
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "your-user-id-here",
  "unitId": "your-unit-id-here",
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Great place to stay! Very clean and comfortable."
}

###
### Get Reviews for a Unit
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/reviews/unit/your-unit-id-here

###
### Get a Single Review
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/reviews/your-review-id-here

###
### Update a Review
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/v1/reviews/your-review-id-here
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "your-user-id-here",
  "rating": 4,
  "comment": "Updated review comment"
}

###
### Delete a Review
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/v1/reviews/your-review-id-here
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "your-user-id-here"
}

###
### Get Unit with Reviews
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/units/your-unit-id-here
